{"tid":815555,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】😵第一城跌穿500萬關口！業主含淚😭劈一成離場","createTime":"2018-09-12T06:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T07:25:44.000Z","uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"398dacbd9b3b8cca010add601773a427977aea8b","tid":815555,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"細價樓跌勢持續，繼天水圍嘉湖山莊後，輪到沙田第一城跌穿500萬元。中原地產黎宗文表示，沙田第一城交投持續放緩，最新錄得37座低層E室成交，實用面積284方呎，兩房間隔，以498萬元沽出，實呎價17,535元。資料顯示，這是繼今年4月以來屋苑首次有低於500萬元成交。同面積細戶上月高位造價近600萬元，低層亦曾逾570萬元，若低層與低層比較，是次賣平一成。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2012年7月以229萬元買入單位，持貨6年，現易手賬面獲利269萬元離場，升值約1.2倍。<br />\n<br />\n記者：朱連峰<br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=9N5G4lBSDNQ9%2FhAsjx6PY%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=cef7ddf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a>"},{"pid":"4a96398acc0477b5e42c60c721632726a3d47212","tid":815555,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"今年4月以來屋苑首次有低於500萬元成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f76da716ebb7d738aae6b420b82fbaf80aa60d","tid":815555,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a96398acc0477b5e42c60c721632726a3d47212","tid":815555,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"今年4月以來屋苑首次有低於500萬元成交<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"first blood<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgm